# Cursor Rules for Agent Skills

This repository contains reusable skills for AI coding agents. When working with skills in this repo:

1. Each skill is a self-contained folder with `SKILL.md`
2. Follow the existing structure: `skills/<agent>/<category>/<skill-name>/`
3. Use YAML frontmatter in `SKILL.md` for metadata
4. Include trigger conditions so agents know when to load the skill
5. Write steps as numbered procedures, not essays
6. Document pitfalls and edge cases

## Skill Template

```markdown
---
name: skill-name
description: What this skill does and when to use it
triggers:
  - keyword1
  - keyword2
---

# Skill Title

## When to Use

## Steps

1. Step one
2. Step two

## Pitfalls

- Don't do X
- Watch out for Y

## Examples

```
